OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mainly cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith some patchy light rain, this
OL,7,Fmainly across the west. Some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells may break through across
OL,9,Fthe east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome rain in the northwest
OL,12,Fthis evening otherwise a mainly dry
OL,13,Fend to the day. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will be cloudy with some patchy
OL,15,Flight rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FMainly dry with some warm
OL,18,Fsunshine breaking through, but the
OL,19,Fnorthwest will be cloudy with a little
OL,20,Frain, especially later on.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
