OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Friday, patchy light rain in
OL,7,Fthe west. Widespread rain will spread
OL,8,Fsoutheast on Saturday followed by a
OL,9,Ffew showers. Mainly dry with bright
OL,10,Fspells on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
